1
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:31,959
How do I break out of this situation?

2
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,120
I still have to send them away one by one.

3
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,760
Mr. Lu.

4
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,879
You've been busy all day.

5
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,920
Have something to restore your energy.

6
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,000
Thank you.

7
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,719
Just leave it here.

8
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:50,079
Shihan is really a nice girl.

9
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,760
An ordinary person...

10
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,519
Who could resist her charm?

11
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,200
Then don't resist it.

12
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:56,719
Oh my god.

13
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:57,879
What am I thinking?

14
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,719
I'm sorry, Mr. Lu.

15
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,280
Have a seat first.

16
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,759
Shihan.

17
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:51,080
Actually, the reason I asked you here today

18
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,879
is to talk to you about something.

19
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,560
The day I called Xu Xuejiao,

20
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,199
you were there too.

21
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:55,719
Right?

22
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:55,919
Ah.

23
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:57,120
What I said to her

24
00:02:57,120 --> 00:03:00,080
was to get her to help treat your mother's illness.

25
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,960
Please don't overthink it.

26
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,080
Shihan.

27
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:15,719
I'm sorry.

28
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,400
Mr. Lu.

29
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,680
I've caused you trouble.

30
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,120
I was overthinking it.

31
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:19,520
It's nothing.

32
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,520
I will definitely work hard from now on.

33
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,520
I'll take my leave now.

34
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,560
Shihan.

35
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,280
No.

36
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,680
I haven't even gotten to the main point yet.

37
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,520
Miss Shihan.

38
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,560
Why are you in such a panic?

39
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,599
Did Lu Chengwen bully you?

40
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,560
No.

41
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,280
Could you stop talking about Mr. Lu like that?

42
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,520
What are you doing here?

43
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,599
Watch your attitude.

44
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:49,120
We came here because of you.

45
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,919
Xuening.

46
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,719
I heard

47
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,800
that your mother is seriously ill.

48
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,680
I have some expertise in medicine.

49
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,080
I can help treat her.

50
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:58,159
Did Mr. Lu tell you that?

51
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,159
Exactly.

52
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,759
He asked me to come pick you up.

53
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:04,479
I appreciate your kindness, Mr. Gu.

54
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,520
Dr. Xu has already agreed to treat my mother.

55
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,800
So please don't trouble yourself.

56
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:12,400
Young Master.

57
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,360
This Jiang Shihan is so ungrateful.

58
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,759
You don't need to take it to heart.

59
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,560
Whatever she chooses

60
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,120
is her own freedom.

61
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,240
Only the Young Master

62
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,959
could be so broad-minded.

63
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:25,920
Qingqiu.

64
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,959
Let's go home.

65
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,000
Gu Zhantian.

66
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,560
You're fired.

67
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,079
You're just a lowly security guard.

68
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,959
Who allowed you to cause trouble here?

69
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:35,199
From this moment on, our engagement

70
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:35,720
is permanently

71
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,560
and completely annulled.

72
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:38,519
Could you stop talking about Mr. Lu like that?

73
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,759
No.

74
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,319
It's Lu Chengwen.

75
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,560
This is too bizarre.

76
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,519
Hello?

77
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,319
Zhao Gang.

78
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,720
Why hasn't Gu Zhantian arrived yet?

79
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,879
Jiang Shihan has already run off.

80
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,920
He was already here just now.

81
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,000
I don't know why,

82
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,720
but he said

83
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,079
there's no need to toy with him anymore,

84
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,519
and left very angrily.

85
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,560
The current plot direction

86
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,399
has indeed gone a bit wrong.

87
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,079
A bit wrong?

88
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,759
Isn't Gu Zhantian the main protagonist?

89
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,680
Then what's up with those four heroines?

90
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,519
They keep hovering around me.

91
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,920
Is that just "a bit wrong"?

92
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,759
If I keep going like this,

93
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,560
tomorrow Gu Zhantian will

94
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,560
kill me!

95
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,720
Sis,

96
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,720
if you have any life-saving items,

97
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,079
you'd better give me one!

98
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:30,560
An item?

99
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,680
I do have one.

100
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,480
This Flash Card

101
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,319
can randomly teleport you

102
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:39,000
to one of the heroines.

103
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:40,000
Sis,

104
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,720
I can barely hide from them as it is.

105
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,319
What's the use of giving me this thing?

106
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,279
Then why not just kill Gu Zhantian?

107
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,279
You can be the male lead.

108
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,759
That way, you won't have to hide anymore.

109
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,600
You want me to go against Gu Zhantian?

110
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,399
You might as well kill me right now.

111
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,480
Lu Chengwen,

112
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,680
in real life,

113
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,480
it's one thing to be bullied everywhere.

114
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,480
But coming here,

115
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,920
are you still going to submit to

116
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,519
Gu Zhantian's tyranny?

117
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,040
Are you

118
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,079
willing to accept this?

119
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,399
I refuse to accept this!

120
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,480
I won't leave it to fate!

121
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,279
I want to...

122
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:11,600
I want to...

123
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,319
I want to help Gu Zhantian fix the plot!

124
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,720
Brother Zhantian,

125
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,199
this is all my fault.

126
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,160
It's my fault for not following the script,

127
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:33,120
which caused the plot to deviate from its original track.

128
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,480
The plot?

129
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,560
Deviate from its track?

130
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,720
Should I take this

131
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,920
as a provocation?

132
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,120
No, no, no, no, no.

133
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:43,959
On the contrary,

134
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,360
I want to help you, Brother Zhantian,

135
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,519
correct the plot

136
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,120
and bring the story back

137
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,319
to its normal course.

138
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,920
I'll help you win back

139
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:53,279
the hearts of those female leads.

140
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,120
Namely,

141
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,279
Leng Qingqiu,

142
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,879
Jiang Shihan, Chen Mengyun, and Xu Xuejiao.

143
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:59,079
The true love of all four of them.

144
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,199
Furthermore, I'll help you

145
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,600
unite the four major families of Haicheng,

146
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,920
including the Lu family.

147
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:05,360
I... I only have one small condition.

148
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,480
Don't kill me.

149
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,199
To be honest,

150
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,720
I don't quite understand what you're saying.

151
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,800
As for killing you,

152
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,079
that's pure nonsense.

153
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,959
I, Gu Zhantian,

154
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:23,480
simply hate evil.

155
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,079
But to those of good character,

156
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,240
I have always

157
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,720
treated them with respect.

158
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,720
Really?

159
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,800
That's great!

160
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,800
It's a deal!

161
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,199
By the way,

162
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:38,079
the Leng family seems to have some financial issues lately.

163
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,480
Brother Zhantian,

164
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,720
you know what to do.

165
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,680
I'll be taking my leave now.

166
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,519
Lu Chengwen,

167
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,800
are you out of your mind?

168
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,720
Young Master,

169
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:56,319
I think Lu Chengwen is setting a trap for us.

170
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,079
Young Master,

171
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,959
the organization just sent a message.

172
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:06,959
There are changes at the border.

173
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,480
You must unite the forces in Haicheng

174
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,360
to secure the rear,

175
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,600
and get the four major families

176
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,680
to work together

177
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,879
against foreign enemies.

178
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,160
Furthermore, I'll help you

179
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,759
unite the four major families of Haicheng,

180
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,079
including the Lu family.

181
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,199
How did Lu Chengwen

182
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:25,720
know that news before I did?

183
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,360
This kid

184
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:31,319
is truly not to be underestimated.

185
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,279
Uncle Leng,

186
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,720
sure.

187
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,480
Then I, Chengwen,

188
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,759
will gladly accept your invitation.

189
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,759
See you tonight.

190
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:54,879
Turn around.

191
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:55,720
Go to the Leng family's place.

192
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:56,720
Yes, sir.

193
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,519
Leng Tianhao invited me to his house for dinner.

194
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,919
It goes without saying that it's about the engagement.

195
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,919
After the engagement,

196
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:07,519
the Lu family will naturally inject capital into Qianfeng Group

197
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:09,080
to help the Leng family tide over their difficulties.

198
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,759
However, I must give this opportunity

199
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,720
to Gu Zhantian.

200
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,879
Make yourself at home.

201
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:17,480
Come, come, come.

202
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,320
Have a seat.

203
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:20,080
Have some water.

204
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,320
Gu Zhantian,

205
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:25,320
if you can understand my hint,

206
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,759
hurry up and come.

207
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,399
Chengwen.

208
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,320
Brother Chengwen.

209
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,279
I'm here.

210
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,720
Leng Qingqiu is dressed so lightly today.

211
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,080
This skirt...

212
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,000
This tank top...

213
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,720
It'd look even better if they were shorter.

214
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,120
This Lu Chengwen...

215
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,279
Has he finally shown his true colors?

216
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,320
Chengwen.

217
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,720
I heard from your mother

218
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,759
that the marriage needs further discussion.

219
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,919
How are your preparations?

220
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,919
Well...

221
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,080
Chairman.

222
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:17,960
Miss.

223
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,799
A Mr. Gu is outside asking to see you.

224
00:10:19,919 --> 00:10:20,919
He says he brings a

225
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:22,480
project that can save the Leng family.

226
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:25,720
I won't see him.

227
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:27,919
Any random nobody

228
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,200
dares to talk big

229
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,120
about saving our Leng family?

230
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,120
No.

231
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,919
Uncle Leng.

232
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,279
Actually,

233
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,720
we must see him.
